      <title>Low Cost Solar Meshcore Repeater</title>
      <link>https://lab.vena.com/meshcore/low-cost-repeater-build/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>youremail@domain.com (Some Person)</author>
